{"tid":729675,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國13個被困洞穴少年，邊個最先出到書，就邊個會成為最大人生贏家","createTime":"2018-07-04T18:10:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T09:51:44.000Z","uid":39316,"like":7,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"25d0a5b5517148ee485ab62fea3efc2e6eabf55a","tid":729675,"uid":39316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T18:10:18.000Z","msg":"全世界都好好奇，13個足球隊少年，無帶入山洞裝備同食物，越走越深，點樣可以係咁既環境下生存到宜家<br />\n13個人如何互相怪責，又互相幫忙；<br />\n由好奇探洞，逐漸變成不安中間既心路歷程；<br />\n大家點樣化解不安情緒，點樣解決衝突，點樣團結；<br />\n面對黑暗環境，缺乏食物，大雨令水位愈來愈高，可以行走同可以訓低休息既地方愈來愈少，去到被發現前一刻，有幾多人仲保持到希望，有幾多人已經絕望，當中大家既對話，點樣鼓勵大家，點樣怪責大家導致呢個困境；<br />\n13個人圍埋一齊，點樣訴說自己出去之後想做既事，自己既夢想；<br />\n<br />\n到大家打定輸數會死既時候，圍埋一齊幻想大家一齊將來既片段<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「我想踢世界盃」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「我都係」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「呢度有邊個唔係」<br />\n「哈哈哈...」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「...我想去美國」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「我都想! 我要去迪士尼樂園!」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「仲有去環球影城!」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「帶埋我細妹去」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「係，佢咁鐘意Frozen一定好開心」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「我都想同我呀爸呀媽搭一次飛機...」<br />\n「......」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「...咁我地要學好英文了，唔係去到唔識同人講野又唔識路牌」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「隔離班有個女仔英文好勁，不如叫佢教我地?」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「係咪呀邊個呀? 咦咪你鐘意果個?」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「咦係呀? 拿，交比你啦，你去搵佢幫我地學英文」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「溝到人地就請我地去美國!」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「仲要食大餐!! 我要食壽司!!」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「食和牛!」<br />\n「......」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「...做咩唔出聲呀? 你未講你第日想做咩喎」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「我老豆想我做醫生，但我唔想」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「做醫生好好呀，點解唔想呀?」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「係囉又多錢」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「又有靚女護士」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「...因為如果想做醫生我就要轉校，老豆話呢間學校程度唔夠高，我又花太多時間踢波...我唔想無得再同你地一齊踢波」<br />\n「......」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「你去做醫生啦」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「咦?」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「你係我地13個入面讀書最叻果個，你一定做到醫生」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「係呀，到你做到醫生，我地踢世界盃果陣搵你做軍醫!」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「仲有記得介紹護士姐姐比我地!!」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 「你成個腦就係得護士姐姐!」<br />\n「哈哈哈哈哈哈....」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你話? 呢個題材，邊個出書會唔發到豬頭咁?"},{"pid":"3fd7f59ba9dcf3b593955efbf0d9643267e79cdb","tid":729675,"uid":144035,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T18:11:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63db50a75690fa1c4156c937ab4db1e82749736a","tid":729675,"uid":77314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:39:32.000Z","msg":"如果係女足同男教練嘅話"},{"pid":"fd056b57c785047c1f175ec56c9fbabd2663a1bf","tid":729675,"uid":77314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63db50a75690fa1c4156c937ab4db1e82749736a","tid":729675,"uid":77314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T09:39:32.000Z","msg":"如果係女足同男教練嘅話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTim